# Task #134/#135: a head whose entries are ALL unresolvable on this card (game deleted /
# different card / no marker-or-twin variant) must degrade to an HONEST empty state — it
# is not "nothing to continue yet" (the head has entries), it is "the list is stale" —
# with the failure logged, and never launch a dead path.
desc Continue dispatcher: head points at a missing file, no variant on card -> honest stale-list state, no launch
invoke ctpak
config paired
sdtext .userdata/shared/Lodor/continue-head.txt	/Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Ghost.gba\tGhost\n
expect_exit 0
expect_trace PRES timeout=4 msg='Continue list is out of date - run Sync in Tools'
expect_trace_absent ENGINE
expect_trace_absent EMULAUNCH
expect_log continue: entry 1 not on card
expect_log continue: no head entry resolvable
